~~ Notification Capstone ~~
This work is for a WPI Capstone Project, and aims to function as a fully developed SDK for aiding in the development of Effective, Accessible, Understandable, and Usable Security Notification.

~~ Installation ~~
Clone the repository:
git clone https://github.com/abmartin25/Notifaction-Capstone.git
cd Notification-Capstone

Install Relevant Dependancies:
This project requires the node.js runtime environment to be present, which is done via an external install
https://nodejs.org/en
Additionally, this project requires:
1. npm install better-sqlite3
2. npm install --save-dev electron@latest
3. npx electron-rebuild -f -w better-sqlite3

~~ Running ~~
To run the basic SDK:
npm start

If get error with npm start run:
1. rm -rf node_modules package-lock.json
2. npx electron-rebuild
3. npm start

To run the testing suite which ensures functionality:
npx playwright test
-- debug: Allows stepping through tests

